{{Infobox_jseries | product_name = J6350 Router | product_image = [[Image:J6350.png|200px|]] | rackspace = 2U | slots = 6: 2 PIMs + 4 ePIMs or PIMs | bandwidth = 2Gbit/s (large packets) 1GBit/s (IMIX) | power = Redundant| cpu = 3.4GHz Pentium 4| memory = 1GB/2GB | flash = 256MB/1GB | }}
Can support the following interfaces:
'''Built-in Interfaces: '''
4 x 10/100/1000 Copper Ethernet
'''LAN (uPIMs - support either PCI PIM or PCI-E ePIM slot)'''
8 x 10/100/1000 Copper Ethernet
16 x 10/100/1000 Copper Ethernet (Double-Height)
6 x Gigabit Ethernet SFP
'''LAN (EPIMs - 4 only): '''
1x1000 (SFP)
1x10/100/1000
4x10/100
'''WAN (PIMs - 2-6 supported):'''
2xSerial
2xT1/E1
1xDS3
1xE3
2xFE
4xISDN BRI (U or ST)
1xADSL2+ (Annex A and Annex B)
2x2-wire or 1x4-wire G.SHDSL
